description:
&lt;p&gt;The following post has become available within KMPT for an enthusiastic, strong customer focused self-motivated assistant administrator.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This may involve shift work allocated on a Monday – Sunday rota basis which would also include covering Bank Holidays and the Christmas period.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidates will be educated to GCSE in Maths and English or equivalent and NVQ Level 2/RSA2 or equivalent and will possess strong customer service skills, a professional and confident telephone manner and good organizational and keyboard skills. They will also require a good working knowledge of Microsoft Office packages which should include strong data inputting ability. The candidate will be able to remain calm and professional when faced with changing or challenging situations. There is also an opportunity for career progression within this role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post may involve contact with our service users.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Prior to interview you will be required to undertake numeracy and literacy tests at a time to be advised; interview dates and times will only be given to those who have successfully completed the tests.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameRosemary HutchinsonTelephone number07824087528&lt;/p&gt;
